{"word":"προσβιάζομαι","slug":"προσβιάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσβιάζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>άσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to compel, constrain</i>, <el>τινα</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>aor1 <el>προσβιασθῆναι</el>, in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <i>to be forced</i> or <i>hard pressed</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}